@startuml User Service Database Schema
!theme plain
skinparam backgroundColor white
skinparam classBackgroundColor lightgreen
skinparam classBorderColor black

title User Service Database Schema

class UserProfile {
  + userId: String (PK)
  + fullName: String
  + phone: String
  + email: String
  + balance: Decimal
  + createdAt: DateTime
  + updatedAt: DateTime
}

note right of UserProfile
  - Primary key: userId
  - Phone: max 15 characters
  - Email: max 255 characters
  - Balance: Decimal(10,2) default 0.00
  - Auto-generated timestamps
  - Maps to "UserProfile" table
end note

@enduml